Package controller.appointment

package controller.appointment
The classes in this package provide the necessary components and functionalities to handle the needs of the Doctor, Patient and Pharmacists in scheduling appointments, recording of the appointment outcomes and viewing it.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AppointmentManager
    The AppointmentManager class provides utility methods for scheduling Appointments.
    AppointmentOutcomeManager
    The AppointmentOutcomeManager class provides utility methods for managing Appointment Outcomes such as recording and retrieving.
